trate this model's\nability to successfully reproduce both BT and FR profiles. The plasma densities\n(6 - 22 x 10$^3$ cm$^{-3}$) and axial magnetic field strengths (2 - 12 mG)\ninferred from our models are consistent with the modeling work of Liu et al.\n(2007) and Jensen & Russell (2008), as well as previous CME FR observations by\nBird et al. (1985).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2016 16:29:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-12"}
