g a tapered\nundulator configuration at the Linac Coherent Light Source. Validation of the\nnonlinear formation is also shown by comparison with experimental results\nobtained in the SPARC SASE FEL experiment at ENEA Frascati, a seeded tapered\namplifier experiment at Brookhaven National Laboratory, and the 10-kW Upgrade\nOscillator experiment at the Thomas Jefferson National Accelerator Facility.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Nov 2016 13:26:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
